      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIGHTY HENRY (4) could manage only fourth at Wentworth Park last time but caught the eye when clocking a fast 29.65 over 515m at this track the start prior. Rates a top chance if runs up to time two back. PINK VENOM (2) failed to come into contention last start at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 3.5 lengths at Taree Super Track (30.80) beating Aussie Wood in a Mix on April 15. The form out of her last race has been franked. Has ability and can measure up. MAXIMUM GAYLE (1) is having her first start around this track. Comes here a last start placegetter at Gosford in a Mix (30.46). Comes through a solid form race last start. Expecting another good run. PULL THE TRIGGER (8) finished in the placings last start and deserves some thought.",
